snippet.title: Foads
snippet.description:
"Welcome to Foads"

Street food around the world - Street Food 2017 - Travel and Food - Market Street

- My channel is dedicated to interesting thing one can see traveling around the world.

- I try record every thing I find interesting in all places I go.

- I hope viewers will share my interests and find the videos fun and worth watching.

We provide Delicious street food, Fruits, Fishing, Vegetables, Weeding Cooking and much more..
That will be helpful for travelers and people who loves food

New videos are posted every week, so make sure to subscribe so you don't miss a video
